	* NEWS, linuxdoc/distcc.sgml: (Cross-Compilation): The
	  recommended convention for gcc names is   <target>-gcc-<version>,
	  and GCC 3.3 will install itself under this   name.  (Alexandre
	  Oliva, Claes Wallin)

